{"TopicId":161559,"ForumId":20,"TopicTitle":"Request: Solar System Supreme","CreatedByName":"The Grand Teki","CreatedById":177895,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-06-04T07:11:55Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"The Grand Teki","CreatedById":177895,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-06-04T07:11:55Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nPlease someone merge (or tell me how to do it) the stock and small \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Real Solar System (mod)\u0022\u003ERSS\u003C/abbr\u003E so it should\u00A0looks like this:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022V2Uu084.png\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 height=\u0022644\u0022 src=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/V2Uu084.png\u0022 width=\u00221024\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\ncorrection: ...same orbits but\u00A0\u003Cstrong\u003Esame time apart.\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\ntest: I will use these acronyms, please don\u0027t take them:\u00A0SSU, SSS\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222017-06-04T10:21:14Z\u0022 title=\u002206/04/2017 10:21  AM\u0022 data-short=\u00227 yr\u0022\u003EJune 4, 2017\u003C/time\u003E by The Grand Teki\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Regor","CreatedById":175796,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-06-04T09:01:16Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nMaybe the modders can put the different planets in L5 Lagrange points of the bigger planets\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"The Grand Teki","CreatedById":177895,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-06-04T09:59:44Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223079940\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022161559\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221496566876\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022175796\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022mabdi36\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n57 minutes ago, mabdi36 said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nMaybe the modders can put the different planets in L5 Lagrange points of the bigger planets\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nPlease explain what is a lagrange point\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Regor","CreatedById":175796,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-06-04T10:06:40Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223079962\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022161559\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221496570384\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022177895\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022The Grand Teki\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n7 minutes ago, The Grand Teki said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nPlease explain what is a lagrange point\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nA lagrange point is, and i quote: \u0022A Lagrange point is a location in space where the combined gravitational forces of two large bodies, such as Earth and the sun or Earth and the moon, equal the centrifugal force felt by a much smaller third body. The interaction of the forces creates a point of equilibrium where a spacecraft may be \u0022parked\u0022 to make observations.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp style=\u0022color:#5b5b5b;\u0022\u003E\nThese points are named after Joseph-Louis Lagrange, an 18th-century mathematician who wrote about them in a 1772 paper concerning what he called the \u0022three-body problem.\u0022 They are also called Lagrangian points and libration points.\u0022\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp style=\u0022color:#5b5b5b;\u0022\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp style=\u0022color:#5b5b5b;\u0022\u003E\nTL;DR, it is the most stable position for objects i.e. Jupiter Trojans / Kepler Telescope\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222017-06-04T10:07:22Z\u0022 title=\u002206/04/2017 10:07  AM\u0022 data-short=\u00227 yr\u0022\u003EJune 4, 2017\u003C/time\u003E by mabdi36\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"The Grand Teki","CreatedById":177895,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-06-04T10:10:08Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223079965\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022161559\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221496570800\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022175796\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022mabdi36\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n3 minutes ago, mabdi36 said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n^\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSo there\u0027d be a lagrange point between our Sun and Kerbol, right?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222017-06-04T10:10:36Z\u0022 title=\u002206/04/2017 10:10  AM\u0022 data-short=\u00227 yr\u0022\u003EJune 4, 2017\u003C/time\u003E by The Grand Teki\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Regor","CreatedById":175796,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-06-04T10:10:34Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223079966\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022161559\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221496571008\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022177895\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022The Grand Teki\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nJust now, The Grand Teki said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSo there\u0027d be a lagrange point between our Sun and Kerbol, right?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYep! Although it would be the barycenter of sun-kerbol and kerbin.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222017-06-04T10:11:32Z\u0022 title=\u002206/04/2017 10:11  AM\u0022 data-short=\u00227 yr\u0022\u003EJune 4, 2017\u003C/time\u003E by mabdi36\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"The Grand Teki","CreatedById":177895,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-06-04T10:11:31Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223079969\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022161559\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221496571034\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022175796\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022mabdi36\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nJust now, mabdi36 said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYep!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nOkay. What do you think of my idea?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Regor","Cre